{"tid":913584,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"join過力威十堂 你唔洗問我答晒","createTime":"2018-11-23T13:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T14:48:52.000Z","uid":209890,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a6cba14a31be22fec8549bb2215f0ad2c758dd76","tid":913584,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:34:22.000Z","msg":"十堂差唔多8千銀<br />\n一上到去sell我一年成六皮野<br />\n上左幾堂無上<br />\n幾年前既事<br />\n最主要唔去既原因係旺角真係冇地方可以拍車<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯一記得係推胸要聞袋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭十堂應該冇教特別野<br />\n全身除左腳之外做一次<br />\n每次做完都跑機一粒鐘<br />\n正常上網都學到既動作 但有人睇住會做得準d應d<br />\n不過你係做得夠重既 飲食岩既 應該大既都會大<br />\n飲食方面會叫個師傅比whatsapp你<br />\n你每餐影比佢 但都係叫你每餐半飯 雞胸 瘦差燒咁<br />\n<br />\n佢果個場地使用年費<br />\n係只可以有教練果陣先比你用佢既健身器材<br />\n依個係佢唯一水人既地方<br />\n有多餘錢可以既試下既<br />\n唔會有靚女捉住你簽幾十年<br />\n窮撚都係自己上網學算啦<br />\n好似館長果d<br />\n自己慢慢感受下"},{"pid":"68223dba6d1df1bb63d8aaedf5e50686a05adfae","tid":913584,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:35:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10d455b8b7b8a12e25786cdf5bbf4bc511dad721","tid":913584,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"真係無操過腳？"},{"pid":"35678d8cb651eff6c7c324f2d4dbcfb9a3b0582d","tid":913584,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10d455b8b7b8a12e25786cdf5bbf4bc511dad721","tid":913584,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"真係無操過腳？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"踩車算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e9fb2b4f544ca39019a7caa52db2c1cb53fb7a","tid":913584,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68223dba6d1df1bb63d8aaedf5e50686a05adfae","tid":913584,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:35:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy